text: Theresa Greenfield is an American politician and real estate developer. She was the Democratic nominee for the 2020 United States Senate election in Iowa. She ran against incumbent Republican Joni Ernst in the November 2020 general election and lost to Ernst. ==References== Category:Living people Category:1963 births Category:Real estate developers Category:Businesspeople from Minnesota Category:Businesspeople from Des Moines, Iowa Category:Politicians from Minnesota Category:Politicians from Des Moines, Iowa Category:Democratic Party (United States) politicians
